highlights.text: “Kung Wala Ka” by Hale has been on Top Songs Philippines the longest, at 443 weeks straight.
“Predador de Perereca” by BLOW RECORDS and Mc Jhey is the highest new entry on Top Songs Philippines at #73.
Cup of Joe has the most spots on Top Songs Philippines. “Multo” is the highest at #1.
“Need You” by Bosx1ne, John Roa, Skusta Clee, Emcee Rhenn, Flow G, Bullet-D, and Kent Mnl is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Philippines, up 67 spots at #129.
